				<cell width="340">
  <color r="255" g="248" b="178">To unlock the gilded panda in challenge or campaign games, you must earn a 5-star zoo fame rating for your zoo.</color><p />

The gilded panda is an extremely elusive creature, with little known about even its most basic behaviour. As a result, this animal will assuredly please your guests. However, only the most experienced zoos are allowed to obtain this rare creature.
						<p/>
To unlock the gilded panda, you must complete the Mysterious Panda campaign.
